data.description: This brand new beauty of a home has been meticulously maintained and includes a large majority of the builders UPGRADES! A beautiful Island kitchen accented with upgraded granite countertops and additional recessed can lighting! Open concept floorplan with upgraded tile wood design flooring throughout the whole first floor, and all bedrooms are located upstairs along with an additional Game room! Extra features include a walk- In pantry, water softener with RO system, and stainless steel appliances!  Get in on this brand new subdivision without the wait! Just a few miles away from downtown Seguin, entertainment such as ZDT's, and Park West for tons of Family fun!
